nd claimed her to be Zulaikha, she covers her face and tearfully leaves confronting Afiya. Later when her face is uncovered she shocks Noor and Imraan's family. || 38:00 || 5 June 2015  \n|-\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#CC9900;\"|\n|-\n| 15 || Hajira is bought back to Afiya by Noor Muhammad, he swears that he will bring Zulaikha back. The Next day Yousuf, on his bike takes Zulaikha to a layer and after visiting the court Zulaikha's divorce case from Imran Moeez in filed. Noor Muhammad goes to Yousuf's home and finds out that Yosusf is Waji Ahmed's Son, and leaves. On their way back Yousuf and Zulaikha are stuck between Noor Muhammad's goons led by Wali and Imran. Yousuf fights for Zulaikha ending up himself being beaten, Zulaikha then strokes a rock on Imran's head who gained every ones attention. After this she helps Yousuf to stand through her support and rushes, the two escape with goons chasing them, after few goons caught them Yousuf hits them and the two are finally successful. Yousuf is now sully sure that Zulaikha loves him. Later Madiha visits Yousuf and Zulaikha and upon Waji Ahmed's insisting she stays there with Zulaikha and Mahrukh for a day. || 38:00 || 12 June 2015  \n|-\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#CC9900;\"|\n|-\n| 16 || Madiha and Tajee insist Zulaikha to live with them for protection, when Waji Ahmed and Yousuf to ask her she agrees. Madiha introduces Zulaikha to her house and both try to bond, Zulaikha is suspicious on her that she once loved Yousuf. Later, Noor Muhammad, and Wali bring their goons at Tajee's home and forcefully beat them, Zulaikha then asks Noor to stop selling her which leads him to raise his hand, Zulaikha faints and is taken back, Madiha informs Hajira about this. || 37:50 || 19 June 2015 \n|-\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#CC9900;\"|\n|-\n| 17 || Zulekha is tied chain and is tortured, while Yousuf is tortured by the police, it is shown that both of them faced torture and are helpless, Zulaikha swears in