f's parents go to Zulekha's home for the marriage proposal when they meet Zulekha they are impressed by her and are hence proud of Yousuf's choice. When Afiya approaches, she and Wali Ahmed (Yousuf's father) are shocked to see each other. The proposal breaks off and a dark past is revealed that Afiya and Waji Ahmed wanted to marry each other and were classmates, but unfortunately Noor Muhammad married Afiya to spoil her life and the same happened to her which Zulekha is going through hence this is the reason why she wants Zulekha to disobey his father is such conditions, it is also told as Noor Muhammad spoiled her life she wants his life to be ruined promising herself that she would never let him marry Buhra. Madiha visits Zulekha's home begging to leave Yousuf, Zulekha proves her how both of them are spending their lives in depression. Madiha calls Zulekha and tells her to marry Imran Moeez for Yousuf.<ref>{{cite web|title=MNYH Episode eleven|accessdate=11 June 2015|date= 15 May 2015|publisher=Review it|author=Fatima Awan|url=http://reviewit.pk/mera-naam-yousuf-hai-episode-11/}}</ref> || 37:30 || 15 May 2015\n|-\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#CC9900;\"|\n|- \n| 12 || Sequences show that Yousuf is being physically tortured at police station and Zulekha is being verbally tortured at her home, Yousuf's mother tells him about the dark past and asks her to leave Zulaikha. Noor Muhammad tells Zulekha that if she doesn't marry Imran Moeez then she would be killed by him, Zulekha tells him that she is not afraid of death but is aware of the pain Yousuf is bearing, she then tells him to release Yousuf and only then she would marry Imran Moeez.<ref>{{cite web|title=MNYH Episode twelve|accessdate=11 June 2015|date=22 May 2015|publisher=Review it|author=Fatima Awan|url=http://reviewit.pk/mera-naam-yousuf-hai-episode-12/}}</ref>|| 37:22 || 22 May 2015\n|-\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#CC9900;\"|\n|-\n| 13 || Episode starts with Yousuf who is surprised to learn tha