ypt]]\n[[Category:Red Sea Riviera]]\n[[Category:Cities in Egypt]]\n[[Category:Tourist attractions in Egypt]]\n", "text_old": "{{for|the song|Sharm El Sheikh (song)}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!--See Template:Infobox gfgvfjcyggjSettlement for additional fields that may be available-->\n<!--See the Table at Infobox Settlement for all fields and descriptions of usage-->\n<!-- Basic info  ---------------->\n|name                   =  <!-- at least one of the first two fields must be filled in -->\n|official_name          = Sharm El Sheikh\n|other_name             = \n|native_name            = \u0634\u0631\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u064a\u062e <!-- if different from the English name -->\n|native_name_lang            = arz\n|nickname               = '''The City of Peace'''\n|settlement_type        = [[List of cities in Egypt|City]]\n|total_type             = <!-- to set a non-standard label for total area and population rows -->\n|motto                  =\n\n<!-- images and maps  ----------->\n|image_skyline          = {{Photomontage\n| photo1a = 8 A resort in Sharm El Sheikh.jpg\n| photo2a = Sharm El Sheikh. Naama Bay..jpg\n| photo2b = \u0645\u062f\u062e\u0644 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u064a\u0629 \u0631\u0623\u0633 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f.jpg\n| photo3a = Al-Mustafa Mosque in Sharm El-Sheikh1.jpg\n| photo3b = \u062a\u0646\u0648\u0639 \u0627\u0644\u0627\u0633\u0645\u0627\u0643 \u0648\u0627\u0644\u0634\u0639\u0627\u0628 \u0628\u0645\u062d\u0645\u064a\u0629 \u0631\u0623\u0633 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f.jpg\n| size = 280\n| spacing = 2\n| color = transparent\n| border = 0\n}}\n|image_caption          = '''Clockwise from top:'''<br> A Resort, Naama Bay, Entrance to the Ras Mohamed Natural park, Mustafa Sheikh Mosque, Fanara Beach\n|image_flag             =\n|flag_size              =\n|image_seal             =\n|seal_size              =\n|image_shield           =\n|shield_size            =\n|image_blank_emblem     =\n|blank_emblem_type      =\n|blank_emblem_size      =\n|image_map      